    <div class="post-grid">
      <article class="post-content">
        <p class="lede-p"><strong>Serpstat is one of the most established names in SEO.</strong> It is also one of the most commonly mis-bought tools in the category — operators sign up expecting traffic and discover they bought a data subscription. After 30 days of hands-on testing — plus interviews with 12 paying customers — here is the honest 2026 verdict on Serpstat: what it is genuinely best at, where the real total cost sits, and the situations where it is exactly the right call.</p>

