          <p><strong>Buy Serpstat if</strong> you are a freelancer, small agency, or business in Eastern Europe — keyword research and competitor analysis are genuinely excellent at one-third Semrush's price. Customer support scores 9.4/10 — tied for highest in the category. <strong>Skip Serpstat if</strong> you need the largest databases, the freshest backlinks, or any kind of content production. Real monthly cost to publish 30 articles with Serpstat lands at $2,469–$7,569 — theStacc does it for $99 flat.</p>
