        </div>

        <div class="callout callout-warn">
          <div class="callout-label">The execution math</div>
          <p>Every Serpstat subscriber we interviewed underestimated this by roughly <strong>20x</strong>. They saw $69/mo and budgeted $69/mo. They actually spend $5,834+/mo to turn that data into published pages. The tool is honest about what it does — the gap is in how customers calculate their <em>real</em> SEO budget.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="inline-cta dark">
          <div class="cta-copy">
            <h4>Wondering if buying Serpstat makes more sense than hiring an SEO team?</h4>
