        <h2 id="pros-cons">Pros and cons after 30 days</h2>

        <div class="pros-cons">
          <div class="pros-card">
            <h4>What Serpstat gets right</h4>
            <ul>
              <li>Keyword research is genuinely strong — Tree View is unique in the category</li>
              <li>10 years of historical keyword data — useful for seasonal planning</li>
