        <h2 id="performance">Performance benchmarks — how Serpstat stacks up</h2>
        <p>Serpstat's data scale is meaningful — <strong>hundreds of billions of links indexed and billions of keywords across 230+ regional Google databases</strong>. Smaller than Semrush and Ahrefs but covers all major commercial markets. Customer support is the standout metric: 9.4/10 on G2, tied for highest in the SEO suite category. Tree View for hierarchical keyword planning is a unique feature competitors do not match.</p>

        <h3>Keyword database size</h3>

        <div class="chart-card">
          <div class="chart-head">
            <div>
              <div class="chart-title">Keyword database size (billions · 2026)</div>
              <div class="chart-sub">Public vendor figures · cross-checked against independent audits</div>
            </div>
            <div class="chart-legend">
              <span class="lg-1">Serpstat</span>
