          </div>
        </div>

        <p>Serpstat's own blog publishes consistently in English, Russian, and Ukrainian — ranking for competitive SEO terms in multiple markets. Worth following for international SEO tactics whether you pay for the tool or not.</p>

        <blockquote class="pull">
          "We compared Serpstat and Semrush for our agency over 60 days. Serpstat handled 95% of our daily workflows at one-third the cost. The keyword Tree View saved us hours of manual clustering. We kept Semrush only for two enterprise clients who specifically asked for it."
